---
description: Ruby Documentation Rules
globs:
  - "**/*.rb"
  - "**/*.md"
alwaysApply: true
---

- Write documentation on English only.
- Document public API with YARD.
- Update README with usage examples.
- Add inline comments for complex logic.
- Maintain CHANGELOG.md following Keep a Changelog.
- Document exceptions and error handling.
- Use RDoc for generated docs.
- Write tutorials for key features in docs/.
